May 2008
     BOPS 3.1
     Added 3rd particle species - protons
     Removed freeze mode

February 2007
     BOPS 3:  Fortran90 version
	- runtime array allocation
     Source code under subversion control
     f77 version no longer maintained

December 2004:
     BOPS 2: CVS version
     Public release on FZJ-Server

-----------
Prehistory:
-----------
August 1995:   
     Relativistic velocity load (2v,3v) and bcs
     Pushers and em field solvers for s- and c-polarisation
February 1994: 
     FT routines for reflected harmonics
     Particle tracking
     Steady-state field diagnostics
August 1992:   
     Mobile ions, double-precision pusher
     Instantaneous absorption diagnostics
     Scaling for boost frame --> lab frame
June 1990:     
     Fixed ions, oblique incidence boost
     

